---
---
<section class="section pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>料金プラン</h2>
    <div class="pricing__plans">
      <div class="pricing__card">
        <h3 class="pricing__title">いつでもケーキ</h3>
        <div class="pricing__price">初期費用 無料</div>
        <p class="pricing__description">注文代金の <strong>5.5%</strong>（税込）の従量課金制</p>
        <ul class="pricing__features">
          <li class="pricing__feature">店頭受取予約受付</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">WEB事前決済</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">メニュー・オプション管理</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">データ出力機能（PDF、CSV）</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">メーリングリストダウンロード</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">在庫管理機能</li>
          <li class="pricing__feature">導入サポート</li>
        </ul>
        <p>※WEB事前決済ご利用時は別途決済手数料3.6%が発生します</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">無料相談・資料請求はこちら</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .pricing {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .pricing__plans {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .pricing__card {
    max-width: 500px;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background-color: var(--secondary-color);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .pricing__title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--accent-color);
  }

  .pricing__price {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .pricing__description {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .pricing__features {
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .pricing__feature {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 30px;
  }

  .pricing__feature:before {
    content: '✓';
    color: var(--accent-color);
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
